                        <h1>Insights report: The Future of Fleets</h1>
                        <p xmlns="">One thing&rsquo;s for sure. Vehicle operators are expecting a busy 2017.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">With 71% anticipating growth over the next 12 months, the European commercial transport industry is optimistic about its immediate prospects.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">But there are bumps in the road ahead.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">Continued economic pressure, stricter emissions regulation, unpredictable fuel prices and growing competition are among the many factors that will continue to challenge the commercial transport industry in 2017.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">We&rsquo;ve conducted a survey with senior managers of some of Europe&rsquo;s top commercial transport companies to give unique insight into the sector&rsquo;s challenges and prospects, and how the industry is responding.</p>

